::KitKat::

She feels herself getting drowsy and closes her eyes.  She knew that 
she couldn't leave her team without a leader, but she couldn't keep 
here eyes open any longer.  Her body felt numb to her and for a few 
moments, she felt no pain.  She listened to the other talk as she 
fell into the darkness of sleep.
